                <l>هذه رساله بولس الرسول الي طيطس</l>
                <l>وهى من العدد ثلثه اعشر</l>
              </orig>
              <reg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                This is the Epistle of Paul the Apostle to Titus.
                And it is the thirteenth in order.
              </reg>
            </choice>
          </head>
        </div>
        <div type="rubric" corresp="Tit2:11">
          <anchor source="#BnF_ar_6725_III" n="8v" facs="https://gallica.bnf.fr/ark:/12148/btv1b8406179n/f27.highres"/>
          <head rend="red">
            <choice>
              <orig xml:lang="ar">
                <l>قراه لعيد قداس الما</l>
              </orig>
              <reg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                Reading of <date when-custom="#SanctificationOfWater">the Feast of the Sanctification of Water</date>.
              </reg>
            </choice>
          </head>
        </div>
        <div type="rubric" corresp="Tit3:1">
          <anchor source="#BnF_ar_6725_III" n="8v" facs="https://gallica.bnf.fr/ark:/12148/btv1b8406179n/f27.highres"/>
          <head rend="red">
            <choice>
              <orig xml:lang="ar">
                <l>قراه لثانى القلند</l>
              </orig>
              <reg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                Reading of <date when-custom="#Epiphany2">the second of Ephiphany</date>.
              </reg>
            </choice>
          </head>
        </div>
      </div>      <!-- Titus -->
      <div xml:id="Philemon" type="Epistle">
        <div type="rubric" corresp="Phlm1">
          <anchor source="#BnF_ar_6725_III" n="9v" facs="https://gallica.bnf.fr/ark:/12148/btv1b8406179n/f29.highres"/>
          <head rend="red">
            <choice>
              <orig xml:lang="ar">
                <l>هذه رساله بولس الرسول الي فليمن وهى تمام</l>
                <l>اربعه اعشر رساله</l>
              </orig>
              <reg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                This is the Epistle of Paul the Apostle to Philemon. And it completes
                the fourteen epistles.
              </reg>
            </choice>
          </head>
        </div>
